# Logs
logs
*.log
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
pnpm-debug.log*
lerna-debug.log*

node_modules
# Keep `dist/` tracked as an empty directory so `//go:embed all:web/explorer/dist`
# in cmd/rpc/server.go always finds a valid target — `npm run build` writes real
# assets here at canopy build time, downstream Go consumers (launchpad, indexer,
# graduator) get a no-op `.gitkeep` and still vendor cleanly.
dist/*
!dist/.gitkeep
dist-ssr
*.local

# Editor directories and files
.vscode/*
!.vscode/extensions.json
.idea
.DS_Store
*.suo
*.ntvs*
*.njsproj
*.sln
*.sw?
